The paper discusses the application of software-defined networks (SDN) in smart grid communication, which falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). The paper also discusses security and privacy schemes, which falls under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the architecture and routing schemes, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). Finally, the paper also discusses challenges and future research directions, which falls under the category of computers and society (cs.CY).
